<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>خ م ش<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٦٧٨ - خ م ش]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>خمَشَ يَخمُش ويَخمِش، خَمْشًا، فهو خامِش، والمفعول مَخْموش<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• خمَش وجهَه:</span> خدشه، جرح ظاهر بشرته <span class="c1">"خَمَشَه قِطٌّ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• خمَش فلانًا:</span> جرحَ بشرتَه في أي موضعٍ من جَسَده <span class="c1">"خمَش خصْمه"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>